Imo camera drones should be restricted in PvP zones. Players using the camera, or their teammates, can be followed in “Follow Mode,” but allowing free control of the drone to explore the entire map is unacceptable.

This shouldn’t apply only to arenas. Within Galia as well, drones should be limited by defense systems that detect and destroy them when they move around. The fog of war should not be violated.
